      "content": "wait i'm not feeling shaky or anything, i just want to be proactive. i usually take 25 units of basal at night to keep me steady, but since i barely ate, i figured skipping it would be safer than taking the full amount. if i skip the 25 units tonight, will that actually be fine or is it really that big of a deal?",
